sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Poll Official
    participant App as Official App
    participant Server as API Server
    participant DB as Database
    participant Auth as JWT Service

    User->>App: Enter username and password
    App->>Server: GET server public key
    Server-->>App: RSA-4096 public key

    App->>App: Generate DEK (AES-256-GCM)
    App->>App: Encrypt credentials with DEK
    App->>App: Wrap DEK using RSA-OAEP-SHA256
    App->>Server: POST encrypted login payload

    Server->>Server: Unwrap DEK and decrypt payload
    Server->>DB: Verify username and password hash
    DB-->>Server: Match or no match

    alt Invalid credentials
        Server-->>App: 401 Unauthorized
        App-->>User: Authentication failed
    else Valid credentials
        Server->>Server: Check active session
        alt Already logged in
            Server-->>App: 409 Conflict
            App-->>User: Already logged in elsewhere
        else Session available
            Server->>Auth: Generate signed JWT (8h)
            Auth-->>Server: JWT token
            Server-->>App: 200 OK + JWT + user profile
            App-->>User: Authentication successful
        end
    end
